comment:
* Class that stores information specific to voice network registration.
 * @hide

variables.name: cssSupported
variables.comment:
* oncurrent services support indicator. if
     * registered on a CDMA system.
     * false - Concurrent services not supported,
     * true - Concurrent services supported

variables.name: roamingIndicator
variables.comment:
* TSB-58 Roaming Indicator if registered
     * on a CDMA or EVDO system or -1 if not.
     * Valid values are 0-255.

variables.name: systemIsInPrl
variables.comment:
* indicates whether the current system is in the
     * PRL if registered on a CDMA or EVDO system or -1 if
     * not. 0=not in the PRL, 1=in the PRL

variables.name: defaultRoamingIndicator
variables.comment:
* default Roaming Indicator from the PRL,
     * if registered on a CDMA or EVDO system or -1 if not.
     * Valid values are 0-255.

methods.name: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)

methodNames: public void writeToParcel(Parcel dest, int flags)
